divs: Sighting DetailsObject was white. Was not an airplane, as there were many airplanes in the area with contrails. It was bulging in the center. It completely disappeared into thin air. It was very visible in the daytime. Object was headed north. We were at home, sitting outside. I think around 5 miles in the air. We were looking at the clouds and sky at some of the airplanes and noticed this object.
Summary: UFO in Ontario, bulging in middle and white
